title: Roger Stone
added: Stone is has been married twice. Once to a woman named Ann Stone from 1974-1990. In 1995 he would marry Nydia Stone, they have 2 children Andria Stone and Scott Stone. Stone said he was raised [[Roman Catholic]] he said that he would eventually fall away from the church. However, after his prison sentence was commuted by [[Donald Trump]] he said he had rekindled his relationship with [[God]].
